# Keycloak writes to /opt/keycloak/data, /opt/keycloak/lib/quarkus, and other
# paths at startup. readOnlyRootFilesystem is not feasible for this third-party
# image without extensive volume mounts that would break on version upgrades.
# Pod and container security context are hardened (runAsNonRoot, drop ALL caps,
# no privilege escalation).
KSV-0014
